TI  - [Intrathoracic hernia after laparoscopic nephrectomy: clinical manifestation and 
      conservative management].
PG  - 1499-502
LID - 10.1007/s00120-009-2107-0 [doi]
AB  - Diaphragmatic hernia can be inborn as well as acquired. We report on the 
      manifestation of an intrathoracic hernia after laparoscopic nephrectomy. 
      Intraoperative and postoperative complications could make intense medical 
      treatment or further surgery necessary. In cases of lasting abdominal discomfort 
      or pulmonary symptoms after abdominal surgery, radiological investigation to 
      exclude intrathoracic hernia should be considered.
